\p
\v 14 \add Is\add* Israel a servant? \add is\add* he a homeborn \add slave?
\add* why is he spoiled? 
\v 15 The young lions roared upon him, \add and\add* yelled, and they made his
land waste: his cities are burned without inhabitant. 
\v 16 Also the children of Noph and Tahapanes have broken the crown of thy
